@yokomodoyokomodo debut album “Strikes Again!” Out Friday, presave link in bio. Bitch Face by @maddienorice and Asshole BF by me out now

YO!KOMODO (@yokomodoyokomodo) started in #college with two of my best friends, @maddienorice and [redacted🐸] amidst an overly competitive music school environment where all we wanted to do was play loud punk shit. While I’ve learned to find that energy in almost every musical situation I am fortunate enough to be a part of, it feels nice to express that in a way that feels true to myself and reminds me why I began this musical journey in the first place. 

Maddie and I wrote 5 songs each and with [redacted🐸] after an almost 10 year hiatus, we got together and recorded everything over a weekend in October 2022. The end result is our debut album, Strikes Again!, out now.  Linkobodo. 

Now someone please book us for your wedding, divorce, funeral, something. Hope you enjoy.

Raveena - Asha’s Awakening (2/11/2022) I fall in love with music again and again whenever Raveena and I are together. Grateful to have been a part of such an expansive and whimsical record, especially with a team of collaborators I’ve had such a long standing relationship with. Rather than stunt our creative flow, if anything, the quarantine from 2020-2021 fueled the rabbit holes we explored together. The myriad of talented producers brought a varied and fresh perspective to the r&b/soul tinted lushness which Raveena and @everettorr had built up so thoughtfully since before we started making music together in 2015.

I highly encourage a top to bottom listen as the full experience of Bollywood colors to ethereal alien soundscapes makes the 15 minute guided meditation at the end hit that much harder. 🌈✨👽⛲️❤️
Sat down with @littlemisscccamelle / @bandwagonasia earlier this year. Thanks for the wonderful writeup and allowing me to go in depth about my passion and roots!

SEP 29 2023: ‘Existential Crisis Boy: Part 1’ out now! Worked on Same Language, ecstatic to be a part of such a cool album. Tyler has always embodied many elements of what I call home base in music: quirkiness, simplicity, and childlike curiosity. The way he threads his pop songwriting and punk rock roots have resonated with me since we met at @zacbrownband’s house over the pandemic. Honored to call him a friend and collaborator. Out on all streaming platforms today!

social_posts.post_text: Honored to join the @jorjasmith_ crew and stand in for the rockstar that is @thomasftotten on Fallon a few weeks back! Thank you @amanesuganami for the call and being such a great leader. Full video available on YouTube. Congrats Jorja on your new album! Go check out “falling or flying” out now.

Thrilled to be participating in a very special soundscape installation Saturday DEC 2 at NAVEL with an amazing group of musicians, dancers, and visual artists. Tickets are still available at purenowhere.shop or in my stories. All proceeds to benefit @thefranciscohomes, providing support to formerly incarcerated individuals aspiring to re-integrate back into the community. This will be my last public performance of the year, come join for a beautiful evening and some amazing food!
